        <p></p>
        <p>Eight major food allergens – milk, egg, peanut, tree nuts, wheat, soy, fish and crustacean shellfish – are
          responsible for most of the serious food allergy reactions in the United States. How serious? Let's take a look!</p>
      </header>
      <ul class="statistics">
        <li class="style1">
          <span class="icon fas fa-hashtag "></span>
